OL,3,C'Die Hard is not a Christmas movie,'
OL,4,Crule British public in new survey
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 1990 American comedy Home
OL,7,FAlone topped the list as the nation's
OL,8,Ffavourite Christmas film, and the 2003
OL,9,From-com Love Actually starring Emma
OL,10,FThompson and Hugh Grant was runner-up.
OL,12,FIt was followed by the 1946 James
OL,13,FStewart classic It's A Wonderful Life
OL,14,Fin third place, with Elf, which was
OL,15,Freleased in 2003, in fourth.
OL,17,FDespite the public's overall ruling on
OL,18,FDie Hard, one in 20 respondents said
OL,19,Fit was their top Christmas film.
