OL,3,C'Die Hard is not a Christmas movie,'
OL,4,Crule British public in new survey
OL,6,FThe survey also found that 17% of
OL,7,Fpeople said they do not have a clear
OL,8,Ffavourite.
OL,10,FMore than two out of five felt the
OL,11,Fmost acceptable time to start watching
OL,12,FChristmas films is from the beginning
OL,13,Fof December, with 13% saying from the
OL,14,Fbeginning of November, and nearly one
OL,15,Fin 10 admitting they enjoy festive
OL,16,Ffilms all year round.
