OL,3,C'Die Hard is not a Christmas movie,'
OL,4,Crule British public in new survey
OL,6,FTim Richards, founder and chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of cinema chain Vue, said:
OL,8,F"Many of our customers see a trip to
OL,9,Fthe big screen over the holidays as a
OL,10,Fchance to sit back, switch off and
OL,11,Fenjoy great stories together - whether
OL,12,Fthat's a much-loved classic like Home
OL,13,FAlone, the high-energy fun of Die
OL,14,FHard, or a brand-new film such as
OL,15,FGurinder Chadha's Christmas Karma,
OL,16,FWicked or Avatar.
OL,18,F"Cinema has always brought people
OL,19,Ftogether, and Christmas reminds us
OL,20,Fjust how powerful that shared
OL,21,Fexperience can be."
